history.content:
If you checked out a card key to access a room in Cory and have not returned the card key, please return the key as soon as possible to 205 CORY. Without keys, other students cannot have access to the rooms. In addition, they cannot be replaced. We are missing 9 card keys and they need to be returned.

We are open from 9 am to 12 pm and 1 pm to 4 pm. If you come after office hours, there is an envelope located near the door, labeled "Return Keys," that you can put the key in as well.
history.subject: Return Cory Conference Room Keys
